              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table is a base table in a Microsoft SQL Server database designed to store information about different types of documents managed within a content management system. Each record in this table represents a unique document type, identified by a primary key, and includes attributes such as the name of the document type and its associated file extension."
